Type: Package
Package: adcp
Title: Format and Visualize ADCP data
Version: 1.0.2
Author: Danielle Dempsey
Maintainer: Danielle Dempsey <ddempsey@perennia.ca>
Description: Facilitates wrangling and analysis of Current data collected
    as part of the Centre for Marine Applied Research's Coastal Monitoring
    Program. (Compatible sensors: Workhorse Sentinel Acoustic Doppler
    Current Profilers.)
